<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/1c331df7-b89e-499f-9bf1-9c562bfea13c> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/3193c9a7-8f50-4af0-b0b6-f05ebaa23393> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
