<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "First-class ADR UI uses reusable artifact service" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/402e5c0b-dc22-4063-84c6-6b9dd954d540> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "codex" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "First-class ADR UI renders graph decisions through a reusable backend artifact service, not API-handler logic. The implementation adds a read-only ADR renderer for ArchitecturalDecision records that mirrors the checked-in ADR skill/script behavior, plus thin REST endpoints for listing ADRs, fetching one generated markdown document, and downloading a ZIP archive. The React UI adds an ADR page with a generated list, markdown preview, refresh, warnings, and ZIP download. The feature does not write docs/adr and does not invoke an agent or LLM; the project graph remains the source of truth." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/242ae2b2-1ff5-42d2-8ca8-c33deefc3d08> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
