<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/2a778f74-725f-4cd7-a389-52f51888795e> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#isMotivatedBy> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Requirement/1ae3b79a-f2c5-41ba-a221-cc79bfe9edc2> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/2a778f74-725f-4cd7-a389-52f51888795e> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/d7ea56d3-a8ef-4dfa-b18b-f28d4ab79458> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/2a778f74-725f-4cd7-a389-52f51888795e> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/b9de95d5-fab2-4b23-ab4c-86759e5f6912> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Fire-event telemetry lives outside the KG" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/6baa075c-db0d-48e0-800a-0cae86603b2a> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Claim: every push-fire and gate-fire logs to an append-only JSONL at .moosedev/fires.jsonl (gitignored) — {ts, verb, host, entity, decision, records_cited} — and never enters the project graph. Fires are operational telemetry, not knowledge; aggregates (e.g. gate prevented N constraint violations in month 2) become knowledge only through deliberate human capture as typed records at trial-review time. Why: this operationalizes Consequence 6505ed72 (v3 is earned by v2's numbers — enforcement value must be measurable) without polluting the canonical graph: high-frequency event streams in kg.nq would bloat the committed, human-reviewed artifact and dilute walk precision for zero curation value. The observations stratum (AD b0d3e4d9) is for measured facts about CODE, instrument-provenanced and commit-anchored — tool telemetry about MOOSEDev itself is a different beast and stays out. Spec: spec/MOOSEDev_v2_spec.md §4.4." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/305f87a8-2658-4c5e-bdb1-6db2408d8c28> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-07T04:50:08.125488Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
