<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#isMotivatedBy> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Requirement/08b807a4-d7fa-4b0a-ad84-78158a4a8088> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/2ff40771-c414-4ec6-ba75-c08ec6982477> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/c882a7f1-ac40-4fa4-9b87-6c37af945d61> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/442f0255-7919-4fc4-9fcd-da1961cfc463> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/b6762624-a76a-4fb2-bb6e-0de8e87d5b9d> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4a86aabc-bd7d-4587-adb2-a051f0386dc5> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/f0d6ea94-7628-446f-8848-eadf8cb4d51c> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Split the benchmark baseline into B1-md and B1-rag" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Refines the arm design of benchmark AD 47f3f038. Prompted by the observation that modern AGENTIC coding tools mostly do NOT use embedding/vector retrieval over code: Claude Code, opencode (our driver), and Aider use agentic search (grep/glob/read) + structural maps (LSP, tree-sitter repo maps); embeddings persist mainly in IDE tools (Cursor @codebase, Continue/Windsurf), and Sourcegraph Cody dropped embeddings. Our B0 confirmed this — it grepped/read, no vector index. Implication: a single 'free-text RAG' B1 is not the most realistic competitor. Two things get retrieved — the CODE (agents grep it) and the captured RATIONALE/why (what MOOSEDev structures). So the free-text baseline is split into TWO arms, both content-parity with B2 (same captured records, different representation): (1) B1-md = the same rationale written as MARKDOWN DOCS in the working tree, consumed by the agent's NATIVE grep/read — the realistic 'team just kept decisions in docs/ADRs' competitor and how agents actually consume docs; (2) B1-rag = a recall() MCP tool over the rationale (BM25 now, optionally embeddings) — maps to the README's literal 'free text + embeddings' memory-tool claim. Headline comparisons become B2 − B1-md (realistic) and B2 − B1-rag (stated claim). This REVISES the earlier 'B1 must be a competent embedding RAG / upgrade BM25 to embeddings' guardrail: embeddings are not the fair/realistic default for a coding agent; markdown-in-tree + agentic search is. Arm ladder: B0 (code only) → B1-md (code + rationale markdown, grep) → B1-rag (code + recall tool) → B2 (code + MOOSEDev graph). User-confirmed 'both'." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-06-18T16:28:45.875304Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4bbb2125-2e2d-4a3f-9ab2-0b3ed55a1864> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Split the benchmark free-text baseline into B1-md (markdown-in-tree, agentic search) + B1-rag (recall tool); reflects how agentic coding tools actually retrieve" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "UUID deep links dispatch to canonical typed record interfaces" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/6baa075c-db0d-48e0-800a-0cae86603b2a> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/8d48edbd-7ee2-4a52-9eac-f2a09c858637> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "codex" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Workbench deep links use durable UUID identity and dispatch records to the same interface users see from the corresponding UI list. ArchitecturalDecision records use #/adrs/{uuid}, Requirements use #/requirements/{uuid}, and Lessons use #/lessons/{uuid}; list clicks, graph-IRI links inside generated artifacts, LSP hover links, and diagnostic codeDescription links all produce those canonical hashes. The SPA resolves each UUID against the generated artifact list and loads the current ordinal detail internally, so generated numbers remain presentation/API details rather than durable identity. The generic #/record/{uuid} route remains the canonical fallback for Constraints, Patterns, code entities, and every kind without a dedicated list interface; legacy generic links to ADRs, Requirements, and Lessons resolve once and replace history with the typed route. This preserves universal workbench addressability and the dependency-free hash router while unifying typed direct-link and list-selected presentation." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasRationale> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Rationale/8f42538f-3c46-4e03-be7d-c700d1ccd2b1> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-10T05:20:33.097334Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "UUID deep links dispatch to canonical typed record interfaces" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/4db59805-ebd6-4209-a564-de6a2656c354> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#supersedes> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/72dc4260-2f0c-47d3-967e-44a981e0c248> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Load repo-root .env before resolving MOOSEDev runtime configuration" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "codex-mcp-client" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "The moosedev binary now loads a repo-root .env at process startup before tracing setup, mode-specific config, MOOSEDEV_DATA_DIR, socket resolution, and autospawn. dotenv values only fill missing environment variables; explicit shell or MCP-client environment values retain precedence. This lets --connect proxies and their detached auto-spawned --serve backend share configuration such as MOOSEDEV_DATA_DIR, MOOSEDEV_ONTOLOGY_DIR, and LLM settings without requiring the start script." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/510c5585-6ff1-4ff1-abff-a7467adc5b71> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-06-18T14:14:46.993364Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
