<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52554569-be1b-4ac0-ad84-0437a758a6b2> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/402e5c0b-dc22-4063-84c6-6b9dd954d540> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
