<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52554569-be1b-4ac0-ad84-0437a758a6b2> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#isMotivatedBy> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Requirement/350c7f2e-61bd-49e4-b7cd-2fdd3f51f521> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52554569-be1b-4ac0-ad84-0437a758a6b2> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/3dd3544c-eb46-4f7a-8764-b0a44813e1b4> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52554569-be1b-4ac0-ad84-0437a758a6b2> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/20807076-c205-4cbb-9bf0-487596f36915> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52554569-be1b-4ac0-ad84-0437a758a6b2> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/b7fd737c-fc3f-4043-8673-403c8897708f> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Densify the graph by GROWL reasoning, not capture" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Materialize entailed A-box edges DETERMINISTICALLY by running GROWL (Trivyn's 97%-coverage OWL 2 RL reasoner) in --enrich mode over the project KG + ontology axioms, rather than asking the capture agent to hand-draw inverses (unreliable + confabulation-adjacent). --enrich does property/subclass propagation — prp-inv (inverses), prp-trp (transitive), prp-spo2 (property chains), prp-spo1 (subPropertyOf), prp-dom/rng — and deliberately skips sameAs (no quadratic blowup; A-box record identity isn't a sameAs problem). Symbolic-pure (invariant #1), no confabulation (only entailments). PROVENANCE: GROWL is sound (\"every output links to a delta triple\") but exposes no per-triple justification API, so materialize into a SEPARATE \"inferred\" named graph — distinguishable from asserted, re-derivable by drop-and-rerun. Complements the capture-workflow fix (base edges): GROWL amplifies base edges, it can't conjure them." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "superseded" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-06-21T23:48:58.183525Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52a6b6cc-cbf0-4b09-ba16-ec3c4f6c90b8> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Densify the graph by GROWL reasoning, not capture" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
