<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Stale-rationale Hint approximated by file-level git history in v2.0" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/CodeEntity/bf05b460-166a-4e43-b5d9-be2d5df42320> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/6baa075c-db0d-48e0-800a-0cae86603b2a> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "The v2.0 stale-rationale diagnostic fires when an entity's newest linked record timestamp predates the last commit touching the entity's defining file (git log -1 --format=%cI per didOpen/didSave, both sides parsed to instants - never string-compared across timezone offsets). Message wording is scoped honestly to the approximation: \"rationale predates later changes to this file\", not per-entity claims. The spec's ideal input - per-entity change counts - is v2.1 observations-stratum data; when that lands, the Hint upgrades to true per-entity churn without changing the diagnostic surface. At most one Hint per entity, severity Hint, individually disableable. First live run caught real drift: the symbol-normalization Constraint (recorded 2026-07-07) predates later commits to symbols.rs." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-09T23:54:45.821104Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Stale-rationale Hint approximated by file-level git history in v2.0" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/4619234e-44dd-4906-9856-03d3a238962b> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/52bb172b-2395-4db5-af14-8166fe313679> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#weighs> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Alternative/ffa7cc72-644c-4d83-9b7d-62d19747afb7> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Project identity in web UI health metadata" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "codex-mcp-client" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "The web UI now identifies the MOOSEDev instance by project, so users running multiple per-project backends can quickly tell which instance they are viewing. GET /api/v1/health includes project_name and project_root derived from the backend data directory and filesystem ancestry: conventional per-project data dirs such as <repo>/.moosedev or <repo>/data resolve to the parent project root, Git ancestry is used when available, and the data dir remains the fallback. The sidebar renders the project name and root path prominently while retaining version/data-dir diagnostics." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-06-20T19:02:54.661031Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/54ca5871-9afb-41c3-b108-7d53bf720191> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Expose project identity in the web UI health metadata" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Split graph module into responsibility submodules" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "codex" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Split graph/mod.rs into responsibility submodules while preserving the public crate::graph::* API. The graph module is now wiring plus PROJECT_KG_GRAPH_IRI and glob re-exports; implementation lives in util, state, capture, relations, lifecycle, query, context, and links. Existing function/type comments were preserved during movement, and short module-level comments were added to explain each boundary. The refactor is behavior-preserving: no external callers changed, no new dependencies were added, and verification passed with cargo build --all-targets, cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings, and cargo test." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-06-22T16:19:28.338208Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/58ff5625-d05b-4dbd-a293-4609a7f8d682> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Split graph module into responsibility submodules" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "First-class Lessons UI via generated-artifact service" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/402e5c0b-dc22-4063-84c6-6b9dd954d540> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/8d48edbd-7ee2-4a52-9eac-f2a09c858637> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "First-class Lessons UI renders Lesson records through the reusable generated-artifact service pattern, the third member of the family after ADRs (AD 242ae2b2) and Requirements (AD 899b9ab9), per the shared-shell Pattern a820e93a. Backend: new src/lessons.rs domain module (LessonSet/LessonDocument/generate_lesson_set) mirrors src/requirements.rs — enumerates typed Lesson records via resolve_class(\"Lesson\"), renders LSN-numbered markdown with a \"Learned from\" source section, an index, warnings (missing_description, unlinked_lessons), and a ZIP archive; thin REST handlers expose /api/v1/lessons, /lessons/{num}, /lessons/archive.zip. Key divergence from the Requirements renderer: the related-sources SPARQL UNIONs both link directions ({ ?lesson learnedFrom ?src } UNION { ?src yieldsLesson ?lesson }) with per-lesson dedupe, because live graph data records the edge from either end; sources are not class-restricted since learnedFrom rangeIncludes both ArchitecturalDecision and AntiPattern. No \"addressed\" analogue — that derivation is requirement-specific. Frontend: LessonsPage wraps the shared GeneratedArtifactPage; Lesson IRI prefix added to LinkedMarkdown so lesson/ADR markdown cross-navigates. Evidence: full cargo suite green incl. tests/lessons.rs + lessons_* API tests; live e2e on this repo's graph rendered 106 lessons (33 with sources) and cross-linked LSN-0037 to AD 059b01b7." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/603fe674-fb52-4bda-81f5-2c5f61b5247f> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-07T07:22:20.401203Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
