<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/899b9ab9-f670-4025-bb26-1c9d046fde01> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/12dcb29d-d40d-4b7e-92c9-8140a155a732> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
