<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dossier silence rule: direct links only, component knowledge secondary" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/CodeEntity/94428221-04c2-41cb-ade1-3e507f5a3feb> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/6baa075c-db0d-48e0-800a-0cae86603b2a> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "phase7-acceptance" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "get_entity_dossier returns nothing (the tool answers with a one-line no-recorded-knowledge hint) unless the resolved entity carries at least one direct, non-deprecated record link; records reachable only through the realized component render as a secondary section inside an existing dossier and never create one. Errors are reserved for caller mistakes (0-based positions, malformed IRIs, bad selectors) - everything the KG does not know is silence, deliberately unlike link_code, which errors because the caller intends a write. The hover surface must not manufacture relevance: a dossier that appears only where someone deliberately attached knowledge keeps precision and trust high." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
