<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/8f20452a-cc92-46ad-bcd4-45f7927f3dae> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/fa20525d-db88-496a-b9d7-1d913c5dc729> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
