<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/91ceb155-4f64-486b-8387-6001daa30a0e> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Trivyn constraint-code task suite spans the non-locality spectrum" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
