<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/b0d3e4d9-873c-4b5b-bff1-0403c6ab1724> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#resultsIn> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Consequence/9c452470-d173-4d47-b26e-9da8f0606c55> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
