<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/b72be9f8-c11c-4b80-89ad-375a559a9c1c> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Path→SystemComponent map lives in the graph, not a config file" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/b72be9f8-c11c-4b80-89ad-375a559a9c1c> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/11e01ea2-f520-4f7c-a165-09532dacd43f> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
