<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/ca1e5be2-308b-40ca-a928-dc286a20695b> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Onboarding: `moosedev init` + curl|sh & Homebrew install channels" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/ca1e5be2-308b-40ca-a928-dc286a20695b> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/402e5c0b-dc22-4063-84c6-6b9dd954d540> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
