<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/d13be5bb-55b0-4ecc-a2c2-78f0ede8f502> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "Claim: the substrate persists exactly the producer's raw output (.moosedev/substrate/index.scip) plus a small meta.json (schema_version, indexed_commit, indexed_at, producer, producer_version, mode, counts), and parses the index into memory on load — no database projection. Why: the moosedev repo index is 3.86 MB / 84 documents / 42,234 occurrences and parses in tens of milliseconds, so a persistent query layer buys nothing; keeping the producer artifact canonical means zero format drift between what rust-analyzer emitted and what the resolver serves. Write protocol: emit to index.scip.tmp, parse+validate, fs::rename into place, write meta.json LAST — meta presence signals a complete substrate. Staleness: meta.indexed_commit vs `git rev-parse HEAD`, baked into every Resolution. The in-memory model (producer-agnostic per-file occurrence tables) is the tree-sitter seam: ResolutionMode { Scip, TreeSitter } exists now, only Scip is constructed. Implemented 2026-07-07 (v2.0 slice 1, commit 8019c5a)." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/d13be5bb-55b0-4ecc-a2c2-78f0ede8f502> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/d13be5bb-55b0-4ecc-a2c2-78f0ede8f502> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-07T19:19:22.80864Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/d13be5bb-55b0-4ecc-a2c2-78f0ede8f502> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Substrate storage: raw SCIP index + meta.json, parsed in-memory" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/d13be5bb-55b0-4ecc-a2c2-78f0ede8f502> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#isMotivatedBy> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/Requirement/350c7f2e-61bd-49e4-b7cd-2fdd3f51f521> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
