<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#ArchitecturalDecision> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "LSP position encoding: negotiate UTF-8, convert UTF-16 via saved files" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/CodeEntity/bf05b460-166a-4e43-b5d9-be2d5df42320> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#concerns> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/SystemComponent/6baa075c-db0d-48e0-800a-0cae86603b2a> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasAuthor> "claude-code" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasDescription> "The Knowledge-LSP negotiates positionEncoding utf-8 when the client offers it (Zed does), making LSP characters equal the substrate's UTF-8 byte columns with no conversion. For UTF-16-only clients, columns are converted by reading the saved file from disk and walking the line's chars (both directions: incoming hover positions and outgoing diagnostic ranges), flooring mid-surrogate positions and clamping past end-of-line. Saved+indexed state is the v2.0 contract: hover and diagnostics reflect the file on disk as of the last moosedev index, with the substrate stale footer and didOpen/didSave-only recompute keeping the drift honest. URI mapping trusts only the daemon's repo root (one daemon per repo), rejects non-file schemes and any path with parent-dir components, and misses are silence, never protocol errors." <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-09T23:54:29.14741Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/e383ce9c-160f-4fca-95c2-5d3ce3ea0b61> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "LSP position encoding: negotiate UTF-8, convert UTF-16 via saved files" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
