<https://moosedev.dev/kg/Lesson/75f622d7-8e77-42e4-b04b-4ecbec731976> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#learnedFrom> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/ArchitecturalDecision/b933bd10-de56-4481-91dd-397a192a8022> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
