<https://moosedev.dev/kg/Rationale/a621fda7-61ce-4b92-bf08-47a143d558fe> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasLifecycleStatus> "accepted" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/Rationale/a621fda7-61ce-4b92-bf08-47a143d558fe> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTimestamp> "2026-07-07T03:29:49.442449Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
<https://moosedev.dev/kg/Rationale/a621fda7-61ce-4b92-bf08-47a143d558fe> <https://trivyn.io/ontologies/software/architecture#hasTitle> "Rationale: One verification pass: subagents don't run the full test suite" <https://moosedev.dev/kg/project> .
